{"tid":1803991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥親身了解交通燈破壞情況","createTime":"2019-12-30T15:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T01:03:50.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c062c29ba825bfc9b38eb87017ca515a5e35e16e","tid":1803991,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:40:40.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥到訪機電工程署及運輸署，了解部門為應對近月示威及破壞行為所採取的措施和善後工作。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，以交通燈設備為例，部門過去多月已更換超過5000個燈號及100個控制器，相當於正常情況下10年的零件使用數量，涉及額外維修開支約3000萬元。<br />\n<br />\n機電署人員向林鄭月娥展示美孚一個被破壞的交通燈控制箱。交通燈控制箱內部的電線被剪斷及焚燒。她向工程人員表示，普遍市民未必立即知道工程人員的付出，但假以時日，會感受到在社會動盪中，城市仍能繼續運作，背後有很多幕後英雄。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥亦到訪運輸署，了解該署監測和處理交通及公共運輸緊急事故的工作，以及推展各項提升專營巴士安全措施的進展。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500225-20191230.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500225-20191230.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=145465b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500225-20191230.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=91ac0b6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500225-20191230.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201280797311565024571ad32a06f9097c886971","tid":1803991,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:41:01.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=84dbc5a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=df2d95e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 暫時最後一個 deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">1/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要29000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=aa5d01cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>美國聯署</ins> deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">3/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要7000人 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhelp-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=2918f987\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">deadline fighters 請出招</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12287cd0381d5a248709bf1ead0ecb448a219faf","tid":1803991,"uid":134294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:41:22.000Z","msg":"果然係戀物狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c16bcccbe6944514